## Workflow

1. Read request → study `docs/` (grep, 1–3 files) — not whole repo
2. **Duplicate** Feature Task Template → fill all sections → link in **📎 Docs**
3. `notion-create-pages` task card → **To do**, Epic + Type, **📎 Docs** relation
4. Return task URL + spec URL — do not implement unless user asks separately

